READ ME
------------------------------------------------------------------

Requires Python 2.7
Install the following to run Python Scripts

sudo pip install beautifulsoup4
sudo pip install -U nltk
sudo pip install -U numpy


To install NLTK documents, in python:
type the following

>> import nltk
>> nltk.download()	

Then an installation window appears. 
Go to the 'Models' tab and select 'wordnet', 'punkt' from under the 'Identifier' column. 
Then click Download and it will install the necessary files. 
Another file you need is under the Models tab, named maxent_treebank_pos_tagger.
